@startuml
title Generate Report Cards Sequence Diagram
autonumber

actor "Homeroom Teacher" as Teacher
participant "Web Client" as Client
participant "HomeroomTeacher" as TeacherClass
participant "Class" as Class
database "Database" as Database

Teacher -> Client: Request Report Cards (Class)
activate Client
Client -> TeacherClass: generateReports(classId)
activate TeacherClass
TeacherClass -> Class: findMany({ include: { grades: true } })
activate Class
Class -> Database: SELECT Students & Grades...
activate Database
Database --> Class: Data
deactivate Database
Class --> TeacherClass: Data
deactivate Class

TeacherClass -> TeacherClass: Calculate GPA/Standings
activate TeacherClass
deactivate TeacherClass

TeacherClass --> Client: Report Data / PDF
deactivate TeacherClass
Client --> Teacher: Display/Download Reports
deactivate Client

@enduml
